---
---

<section class="services" id="services" aria-labelledby="services-title">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="section-num">01</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="services-title">Three parts, <em>one studio.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-lede">
      Wallpaper is having a moment, but choosing it, ordering the right yardage,
      and hanging it without seams or bubbles is genuinely hard. We handle all
      three, so you don't end up with a half-finished project or a roll you're
      afraid to open.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service reveal">
      <span class="service-num" aria-hidden="true">i.</span>
      <svg class="service-icon" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" aria-hidden="true">
        <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="12"/>
        <path d="M30 30 L42 42"/>
        <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="4"/>
      </svg>
      <h3>Source.</h3>
      <p>
        Margaret has a working knowledge of the wallpaper world — from heritage
        houses like Morris &amp; Co. and Schumacher to independent designers and
        grasscloth specialists. Send a mood, a room, or a Pinterest board. You'll
        get real options, not a link dump.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="service reveal">
      <span class="service-num" aria-hidden="true">ii.</span>
      <svg class="service-icon" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M8 40 L24 8 L40 40 Z"/>
        <path d="M14 30 L34 30"/>
      </svg>
      <h3>Style.</h3>
      <p>
        Scale, light, pattern repeat, and existing trim all matter more than a
        swatch can tell you. We help you find a paper that's genuinely right
        for your room — not just one that looked good on a screen.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="service reveal">
      <span class="service-num" aria-hidden="true">iii.</span>
      <svg class="service-icon" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M8 8 L40 8 L40 40 L8 40 Z"/>
        <path d="M8 16 L40 16"/>
        <path d="M16 16 L16 40"/>
        <path d="M24 4 L24 12"/>
      </svg>
      <h3>Hang.</h3>
      <p>
        The part most installers don't want: ceilings, powder rooms with a
        dozen fixtures, grasscloth that shows every seam. This is where the
        job is actually won or lost, and it's the part we love most.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    padding: 140px 40px 120px;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--rule);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .service {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 50px 40px 60px;
    position: relative;
    transition: background 0.4s ease;
  }
  .service:hover { background: var(--paper); }

  .service-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .service h3 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 36px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .service p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .service-num {
    position: absolute;
    top: 30px;
    right: 30px;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .services { padding: 80px 20px; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
